702309f-a.title: Brooklyn: 3rd Street (South) - Bedford Avenue
702309f-a.text:
South 3rd Street, at the N.E. corner of Bedford Ave. These buildings
were still standing in (1929).
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

702310f-a.title: Brooklyn: 3rd Street (South) - Bedford Avenue
702310f-a.text:
South 3rd Street, north side, east from No. 139, just east of Bedford
Ave. At the left foreground is the Industrial School; beyond which is
seen the South 3rd Street Presbyterian Church. Beyond the white building
is Public School No. 50.
September 10, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
